doc.after: As of April 2015 the Brussels Airlines fleet consists of the following aircraft 22  Brussels Airlines previously operated 6 BAe 146 200s These aircraft exited service in 2008 and 4 of them were up for sale Two of them OO DJG OO DJH have been sold One of them OO DJE is still stored at Brussels Airport Two other OO DJJ OO MJE were mentioned for AirDC but that project has been cancelled Instead they went to the new airline Brussels Airlines together with other investors has started in Congo Korongo The last remaining OO DJF has been scrapped
